{"tid":2374890,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★股災預言家警告：散戶沉醉泡沫之中　結局恐暴冧最少50%","createTime":"2021-01-21T14:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T06:09:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":39,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"58683a30513a72bc8305376eb9c88158272b127a","tid":2374890,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"外媒報道，國際知名逆向投資者、曾準確預言過去兩次特大危機、被傳媒譽為「傳奇災難預言家」的GMO資產管理創辦人Jeremy Grantham再度發出警告，稱華爾街正處於泡沫之中，散戶也沉醉其中。<br />\n<br />\nJeremy Grantham指出，近幾個月來，股市的瘋狂和美股飆升正在演變成「史詩般的泡沫」，散戶變得欣喜若狂，四處借錢交易更多的股票。他又警告一直以來，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>牛市都會以泡沫破滅後下跌至少50%而告終</strong></span>，但引發這種暴跌的催化劑「難以預測」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210121/bkn-20210121192156745-0121_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210121%2Fbkn-20210121192156745-0121_00842_001.html&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=4007ef0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210121/bkn-20210121192156745-0121_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9a3b6a9fbe8e60cdcfa3ec65a3d467c8a901ec1c","tid":2374890,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1df16af3ec939ef3d6381c1f98e2dc1e84b929","tid":2374890,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face